{"tid":1692122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑 「一切從馬克思開始」","createTime":"2019-11-04T02:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T02:56:59.000Z","uid":25105,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be46258b372d7937f35db74c4fc1f767d70ff41c","tid":1692122,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lqzqr4BEqt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dlqzqr4BEqt0&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=e1bd8625\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lqzqr4BEqt0</a><br />\n《齊上齊學》19/10 第三講 - 陶傑 「一切從馬克思開始」<br />\n<br />\n陶傑簡略講左馬克思思想既<ins>誕生</ins>，思想去到中俄既<ins>演化</ins>，同中共近代思想滲透既<ins>發展</ins>。<br />\n大家除左行出黎抗爭之外，平時多D為思想做好準備，例如睇論暴政同齊上齊學，為自己補充番抗爭既意義。<br />\n只有思想上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">買足gear</span></strong>，先至可以係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰入面堅持</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b2ed7d8e84766f299cd275e14c0b0edb2224f0c0","tid":1692122,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"只有思想上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">買足gear</span></strong>，先至可以係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰入面堅持</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ccedb5501c74833cf7b8368adbe2a4cfb2e9f6d1","tid":1692122,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"只有思想上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">買足gear</span></strong>，先至可以係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰入面堅持</span></strong>"},{"pid":"bac4a0f32532079aa92e747be0cc7237b2ca3bc6","tid":1692122,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"簡單一句，有春袋揸定唔揸？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692056</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5580dcfbc9017a529ef01f78ad6353f524dd7e55","tid":1692122,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201